value.value:
SELECT prt.ProcessRunlogId,'RerunFailed' as ProcessStatus,exp_val.ProcessLayer as SourceLayer,exp_val.BusinessName,exp_val.ObjectName,
exp_val.FileName,exp_val.SchemaFileName,exp_val.LoadedTimeStamp,scr.SourceName,
scr.SourceObjectName,scr.Format,scr.Source,scr.ProcessType,scr.SourcePath,scr.LandingRawPath,scr.RawObjectName
,scr.RawPath,scr.StageObjectName,scr.StagePath,scr.RejectedObjectName,scr.RejectedPath,scr.CuratedObjectName,scr.CuratedPath,scr.ActiveInd,scr.LoadFormat,
trim(scr.DelimiterInd) as DelimiterInd,trim(scr.HeaderInd) as HeaderInd,trim(scr.SchemaFileInd) as SchemaFileInd
FROM diqcntrlframework.CntlMetadataFilelog exp_val INNER JOIN diqcntrlframework.SourceCntlMetadata scr 
on exp_val.BusinessName = scr.BusinessName and exp_val.ObjectName = scr.ObjectName 
INNER JOIN diqcntrlframework.PipelineRunlog prt 
on prt.BusinessName = scr.BusinessName 
and prt.ObjectName = scr.ObjectName 
and prt.FileName = exp_val.FileName
where scr.ActiveInd = 'Y' and scr.BusinessName = 'SAP_LIMS' and exp_val.status = 'Success'  and (prt.ProcessFlag ='0' or prt.ProcessFlag is null or prt.Status = 'Error')
and exp_val.ProcessType='pull' and prt.TargetLayer IN ('Curated')

SELECT NULL as ProcessRunlogId,'StartNew' as ProcessStatus,exp_val.ProcessLayer as SourceLayer,exp_val.BusinessName,exp_val.ObjectName,exp_val.FileName,
exp_val.SchemaFileName,exp_val.LoadedTimeStamp,scr.SourceName,scr.SourceObjectName,scr.Format,scr.Source,scr.ProcessType,scr.SourcePath,scr.LandingRawPath,
scr.RawObjectName,scr.RawPath,scr.StageObjectName,scr.StagePath,scr.RejectedObjectName,scr.RejectedPath,scr.CuratedObjectName ,scr.CuratedPath,scr.ActiveInd,
scr.LoadFormat,trim(scr.DelimiterInd) as DelimiterInd,trim(scr.HeaderInd) as HeaderInd,trim(scr.SchemaFileInd) as SchemaFileInd
FROM diqcntrlframework.CntlMetadataFilelog exp_val 
INNER JOIN diqcntrlframework.SourceCntlMetadata scr 
on exp_val.BusinessName = scr.BusinessName and exp_val.ObjectName = scr.ObjectName
where exp_val.FileName NOT IN 
(select FileName from diqcntrlframework.PipelineRunlog where TargetLayer IN ('Curated') and (status = 'Success' or ProcessFlag IN ('1', '-1')) and BusinessName = 'SAP_LIMS' group by FileName) and 
exp_val.FileName NOT IN 
(select FileName from diqcntrlframework.PipelineRunlog where TargetLayer='Stage' and ProcessFlag IN ('0','-1') and BusinessName = 'SAP_LIMS' group by FileName)
and scr.ActiveInd = 'Y' and scr.BusinessName = 'SAP_LIMS' and status = 'Success' and exp_val.ProcessType='pull' order by FileName
